track_notes:
This is the TrackBack info off my GPS. Good parking at start and initial pleasant walk through regenerating native woods. 

Once past Point#213 on the route shown fairly grassy to summit which is flat with Cairn & Trigpoint with theodolite screw missing.

If you have time you may wish to include WS-265 on your return. Best approached from NE end then descend via SW to re-join your original route at NH 20738 24765.

Take care and enjoy yourself.

73

Jack(;>J
